{
  "texts": [
    "By learning representations of high-level semantic information in images, they achieve object classification and localization.",
    "These algorithms significantly improve detection accuracy and efficiency in traffic scenarios and demonstrate strong adaptability to different detection environments [6].",
    "Comparison with Previous ReviewsThe basics of this study have been thoroughly reviewed, and the progress of the in-depth study of object detection equipment and its use in traffic scenes has been completed.",
    "In recent years, several researchers have published numerous reviews on object detection, including general object detection [7][8][9][10][11].",
    "These works offer a comprehensive, systematic, and thorough examination of the field."
  ]
}